[SN]TITLE[SN]
Van driver dies in M20 truck crash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A driver has died in a crash between a van and a truck on the M20, close to the junction with the M26.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The collision happened just after 22:00 GMT on Thursday on the London-bound carriageway between junctions four and three.
The van caught fire and the driver was reported to have been unable to escape the vehicle, Kent Police said.
Emergency services arrived and the driver was declared dead at the scene.
